    "title": {
      "rendered": "YouTube Giving Tools: What Your Nonprofit Needs to Know"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://youtube-creators.googleblog.com/2018/08/introducing-youtube-giving-new-tools.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22585\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-Giving-Tools-for-Nonprofits-Twitter.jpg?resize=600%2C315\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-Giving-Tools-for-Nonprofits-Twitter.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-Giving-Tools-for-Nonprofits-Twitter.jpg?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Currently in beta, <a href=\"https://youtube-creators.googleblog.com/2018/08/introducing-youtube-giving-new-tools.html\"><strong>YouTube has released a new suite of giving tools</strong></a> for a small number of nonprofits in the U.S., however, in the coming coming weeks the company will roll out the tools to all 501(c)(3) nonprofit organizations. If your organization would like to get access to the tools as they roll out, make sure you have signed up for the <a href=\"https://www.google.com/nonprofits/\"><strong>Google for Nonprofits Program</strong></a>. Odds are the tools will roll out eventually to <a href=\"https://support.google.com/nonprofits/answer/3215869?hl=en&amp;ref_topic=3247288\"><strong>organizations in other countries who participate in Google for Nonprofits</strong></a>.</p>\n<p>For now, and perhaps always, YouTube is covering the donation processing fees and the tools are as follows:</p>\n<h2>1. Fundraisers</h2>\n<p>Fundraisers allow individuals to donate to creator-led campaigns directly on YouTube via a \u201cDonate\u201d button.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7xkh30Hb42Y\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22587\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-donate-program-hope-for-paws.jpg?resize=600%2C349\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-donate-program-hope-for-paws.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-donate-program-hope-for-paws.jpg?resize=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7xkh30Hb42Y\"><strong>youtube.com/hopeforpaws</strong></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7xkh30Hb42Y\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22590\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-donate-program-thank-you-1.jpg?resize=520%2C405\" alt=\"\" width=\"520\" height=\"405\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-donate-program-thank-you-1.jpg?w=520&amp;ssl=1 520w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-donate-program-thank-you-1.jpg?resize=300%2C234&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 520px) 100vw, 520px\" /></a><strong>Donations Processed by <a href=\"https://www.networkforgood.com/\">Network for Good</a></strong></p>\n<h2>2. Community Fundraisers</h2>\n<p>Community Fundraisers\u00a0enable multiple creators to co-host the same fundraiser. Community Fundraisers appear on all participating creators\u2019 videos at the same time and reflect the collective amount of money raised together.</p>\n<h2>3. Campaign Matching</h2>\n<p>YouTube will show matching pledges from individuals and brands within a Fundraiser. The feature is scheduled to arrive in the coming weeks.</p>\n<h2>4. Super Chat for Good</h2>\n<p>Super Chat enables individuals and creators to interact during live chat and individuals can purchase Super Chats to highlight their messages within chat. Now, when an\u00a0<a href=\"https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/9080764\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>eligible</strong> creator</a>\u00a0enables Super Chat for Good, 100% of Super Chat for Good purchases will be automatically routed to a qualifying nonprofit chosen by the creator.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22584\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-Super-Chat-for-Good.jpg?resize=600%2C321\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-Super-Chat-for-Good.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/YouTube-Super-Chat-for-Good.jpg?resize=300%2C161&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Download the 2018 Global NGO Technology Report!</h2>\n<p>Published in \u0627\u0644\u0639\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651\u0629, English, fran\u00e7ais, portugu\u00eas y espa\u00f1ol, the <strong><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo\">2018 Global NGO Technology Report</a></strong>\u00a0is based on the survey results of 5,352 NGOs from 164 countries.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22066\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blog.jpg?resize=600%2C315\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blog.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blog.jpg?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"//downloads.mailchimp.com/js/signup-forms/popup/embed.js\" data-dojo-config=\"usePlainJson: true, isDebug: false\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\">require([\"mojo/signup-forms/Loader\"], function(L) { L.start({\"baseUrl\":\"mc.us12.list-manage.com\",\"uuid\":\"e9d227595303f56fb14c8ddb7\",\"lid\":\"ab11574089\"}) })</script></p>\n",
